    <div>
        <h2>About My Hobby</h2>
        <p>Photography is not just a hobby for me; it's a way to capture the essence of moments that will last a lifetime. From the grandeur of landscapes to the subtle expressions of wildlife, every photograph tells a story. My journey in photography began many years ago, and it has since become an integral part of my life, allowing me to express my creativity and connect with the world in a profound way.</p>
        <p>Through my lens, I strive to bring out the unseen angles of our everyday world. It's about sharing a perspective that goes unnoticed, telling stories that are unheard, and celebrating the diversity and beauty of life on our planet.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
    <!-- explanation of the services that are offered -->
        <h2>Services Offered</h2>
        <p>Are you looking for stunning photographs to capture your special moments or need professional shots for your next project? I offer a range of photography services tailored to your needs:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Event Photography: Capturing memorable moments of your special events.</li>
            <li>Landscape Commissions: Bringing the beauty of landscapes into your home or office.</li>
            <li>Wildlife Photo Expeditions: Join me on a journey to photograph wildlife in their natural habitats.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Contact me to discuss how we can bring your vision to life through photography.</p>
